{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:1","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.014.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Abijam et Asa, rois de Juda. \u2014 Nadab, Baescha, \u00c9la, Zimri, Omri, rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-8: cf. 2 Ch 13. Ps 103:17.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    La dix-huiti\u00e8me ann\u00e9e du r\u00e8gne de J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath, Abijam r\u00e9gna sur Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.2","name":"1 Rois 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.31","name":"1 Rois 14:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.14.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il r\u00e9gna trois ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Maaca, fille d\u2019Abisalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.3","name":"1 Rois 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.1","name":"1 Rois 15:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Il se livra \u00e0 tous les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s que son p\u00e8re avait commis avant lui; et son c\u0153ur ne fut point tout entier \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, son Dieu, comme l\u2019avait \u00e9t\u00e9 le c\u0153ur de David, son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.4","name":"1 Rois 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.2","name":"1 Rois 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Mais \u00e0 cause de David, l\u2019\u00c9ternel, son Dieu, lui donna une lampe \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, en \u00e9tablissant son fils apr\u00e8s lui et en laissant subsister J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.5","name":"1 Rois 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.3","name":"1 Rois 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Car David avait fait ce qui est droit aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et il ne s\u2019\u00e9tait d\u00e9tourn\u00e9 d\u2019aucun de ses commandements pendant toute sa vie, except\u00e9 dans l\u2019affaire d\u2019Urie, le H\u00e9thien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.6","name":"1 Rois 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.4","name":"1 Rois 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il y eut guerre entre Roboam et J\u00e9roboam, tant que v\u00e9cut Roboam.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.7","name":"1 Rois 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.5","name":"1 Rois 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Le reste des actions d\u2019Abijam, et tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois de Juda? Il y eut guerre entre Abijam et J\u00e9roboam.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.8","name":"1 Rois 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.6","name":"1 Rois 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Abijam se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res, et on l\u2019enterra dans la ville de David. Et Asa, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.9","name":"1 Rois 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.7","name":"1 Rois 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.010,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 9-15: cf. 2 Ch 14; 15. Ps 119:5, 9-11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>La vingti\u00e8me ann\u00e9e de J\u00e9roboam, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, Asa r\u00e9gna sur Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.10","name":"1 Rois 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.8","name":"1 Rois 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Il r\u00e9gna quarante et un ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Maaca, fille d\u2019Abisalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.11","name":"1 Rois 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.9","name":"1 Rois 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Asa fit ce qui est droit aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, comme David, son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.12","name":"1 Rois 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.10","name":"1 Rois 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Il \u00f4ta du pays les prostitu\u00e9s, et il fit dispara\u00eetre toutes les idoles que ses p\u00e8res avaient faites.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.13","name":"1 Rois 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.11","name":"1 Rois 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Et m\u00eame il enleva la dignit\u00e9 de reine \u00e0 Maaca, sa m\u00e8re, parce qu\u2019elle avait fait une idole pour Astart\u00e9. Asa abattit son idole, et la br\u00fbla au torrent de C\u00e9dron.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.14","name":"1 Rois 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.12","name":"1 Rois 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Mais les hauts lieux ne disparurent point, quoique le c\u0153ur d\u2019Asa f\u00fbt en entier \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel pendant toute sa vie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.15","name":"1 Rois 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.13","name":"1 Rois 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Il mit dans la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel les choses consacr\u00e9es par son p\u00e8re et par lui-m\u00eame, de l\u2019argent, de l\u2019or et des vases.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.16","name":"1 Rois 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.14","name":"1 Rois 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.017,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 16-24: cf. 2 Ch 16. J\u00e9 17:5.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Il y eut guerre entre Asa et Baescha, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, pendant toute leur vie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.17","name":"1 Rois 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.15","name":"1 Rois 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Baescha, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, monta contre Juda; et il b\u00e2tit Rama, pour emp\u00eacher ceux d\u2019Asa, roi de Juda, de sortir et d\u2019entrer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.18","name":"1 Rois 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.16","name":"1 Rois 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Asa prit tout l\u2019argent et tout l\u2019or qui \u00e9taient rest\u00e9s dans les tr\u00e9sors de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et les tr\u00e9sors de la maison du roi, et il les mit entre les mains de ses serviteurs qu\u2019il envoya vers Ben-Hadad, fils de Thabrimmon, fils de Hezjon, roi de Syrie, qui habitait \u00e0 Damas. Le roi Asa lui fit dire:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.19","name":"1 Rois 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.17","name":"1 Rois 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.19","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:19","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Qu\u2019il y ait une alliance entre moi et toi, comme il y en eut une entre mon p\u00e8re et ton p\u00e8re. Voici, je t\u2019envoie un pr\u00e9sent en argent et en or. Va, romps ton alliance avec Baescha, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, afin qu\u2019il s\u2019\u00e9loigne de moi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.20","name":"1 Rois 15:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.18","name":"1 Rois 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.20","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:20","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Ben-Hadad \u00e9couta le roi Asa; il envoya les chefs de son arm\u00e9e contre les villes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et il battit Ijjon, Dan, Abel-Beth-Maaca, tout Kinneroth, et tout le pays de Nephthali.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.21","name":"1 Rois 15:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.19","name":"1 Rois 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.21","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:21","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Lorsque Baescha l\u2019apprit, il cessa de b\u00e2tir Rama, et il resta \u00e0 Thirtsa.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.22","name":"1 Rois 15:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.20","name":"1 Rois 15:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.22","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:22","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Le roi Asa convoqua tout Juda, sans exempter personne, et ils emport\u00e8rent les pierres et le bois que Baescha employait \u00e0 la construction de Rama; et le roi Asa s\u2019en servit pour b\u00e2tir Gu\u00e9ba de Benjamin et Mitspa.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.23","name":"1 Rois 15:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.21","name":"1 Rois 15:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.23","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:23","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Le reste de toutes les actions d\u2019Asa, tous ses exploits et tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, et les villes qu\u2019il a b\u00e2ties, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois de Juda? Toutefois, \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9poque de sa vieillesse, il eut les pieds malades.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.24","name":"1 Rois 15:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.22","name":"1 Rois 15:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.24","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:24","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Asa se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res, et il fut enterr\u00e9 avec ses p\u00e8res dans la ville de David, son p\u00e8re. Et Josaphat, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.25","name":"1 Rois 15:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.23","name":"1 Rois 15:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.25","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:25","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.026,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 25-32: cf. 1 R 14:7-16. No 23:19. Ec 8:11-13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Nadab, fils de J\u00e9roboam, r\u00e9gna sur Isra\u00ebl, la seconde ann\u00e9e d\u2019Asa, roi de Juda. Il r\u00e9gna deux ans sur Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.26","name":"1 Rois 15:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.24","name":"1 Rois 15:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.26","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:26","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel; et il marcha dans la voie de son p\u00e8re, se livrant aux p\u00e9ch\u00e9s que son p\u00e8re avait fait commettre \u00e0 Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.27","name":"1 Rois 15:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.25","name":"1 Rois 15:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.27","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:27","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Baescha, fils d\u2019Achija, de la maison d\u2019Issacar, conspira contre lui, et Baescha le tua \u00e0 Guibbethon, qui appartenait aux Philistins, pendant que Nadab et tout Isra\u00ebl assi\u00e9geaient Guibbethon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.28","name":"1 Rois 15:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.26","name":"1 Rois 15:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.28","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:28","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Baescha le fit p\u00e9rir la troisi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Asa, roi de Juda, et il r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.29","name":"1 Rois 15:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.27","name":"1 Rois 15:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.29","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:29","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019il fut roi, il frappa toute la maison de J\u00e9roboam, il n\u2019en laissa \u00e9chapper personne et il d\u00e9truisit tout ce qui respirait, selon la parole que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait dite par son serviteur Achija de Silo,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.30","name":"1 Rois 15:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.28","name":"1 Rois 15:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.30","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:30","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>\u00e0 cause des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s que J\u00e9roboam avait commis et qu\u2019il avait fait commettre \u00e0 Isra\u00ebl, irritant ainsi l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.31","name":"1 Rois 15:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.29","name":"1 Rois 15:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.31","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:31","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Le reste des actions de Nadab, et tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.32","name":"1 Rois 15:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.30","name":"1 Rois 15:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.32","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:32","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Il y eut guerre entre Asa et Baescha, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, pendant toute leur vie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.33","name":"1 Rois 15:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.31","name":"1 Rois 15:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.33","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:33","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.034,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">15 v. 33 \u00e0 16 v. 7: cf. 1 R 14:7-11, 14; 21:20-24. (2 R 17:13, 14. J\u00e9 11:7, 8.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>La troisi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Asa, roi de Juda, Baescha, fils d\u2019Achija, r\u00e9gna sur tout Isra\u00ebl \u00e0 Thirtsa. Il r\u00e9gna vingt-quatre ans.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.34","name":"1 Rois 15:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.32","name":"1 Rois 15:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.34","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 15:34","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.015.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.016.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.15.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et il marcha dans la voie de J\u00e9roboam, se livrant aux p\u00e9ch\u00e9s que J\u00e9roboam avait fait commettre \u00e0 Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15","name":"1 Rois 15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.1","name":"1 Rois 16:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.16.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.33","name":"1 Rois 15:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.15.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbdb